         "4.0",
         "61.0",
         "Details\nIn late June 2025, Iran-aligned hacktivist groups launched distributed-denial-of-service (DDoS) attacks, targeting U.S. networks. More than 1100 internet protocol (IP) addresses conducting DDoS attacks were associated with hacktivist group Mr. Hamza Group1. The full list of indicators of compromise (IOCs) are available via the U.S. Department of Treasury’s Project Fortress Automated Threat Information Feed. Additionally, an excel file of the IOCs have been disseminated with this notice.",
